	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">今日娱乐：小丑女要再拍电影，《帝企鹅日记》有续集</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-17 10:12:13 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">3</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">9</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

